397
00:15:39.655 --> 00:15:43.335
Mas los dioses no nos otorgaron tamaña ventura,

398
00:15:43.335 --> 00:15:45.255
ni á mi padre ni á mí, y

399
00:15:45.255 --> 00:15:46.615
ahora es preciso

400
00:15:46.935 --> 00:15:48.295
